    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ignifugo</strong> is a top-down <strong>action-roguelike</strong> with elements borrowed from the <strong>auto-battler</strong> genre. Choose your path through biomes with <strong>procedurally generated maps</strong> as you control a <strong>combat shell</strong> with slots for placing <strong>upgradable units</strong> of different <strong>classes</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/3128d3ff0fcfff56bfa1906847ef2f90.avif?t=1772203198\" width=1560 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/969091c33181e0a942c47098b8e788bb.poster.avif?t=1772203198\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/969091c33181e0a942c47098b8e788bb.webm?t=1772203198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/969091c33181e0a942c47098b8e788bb.mp4?t=1772203198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select <strong>shells</strong> and <strong>unlock</strong> new ones. If you defeat <strong>THE FLAME</strong> with a shell you unlock <strong>difficulty levels</strong>: <strong>incandescence</strong>. They add modifiers to the run, from enemy health variation to influencing map generation.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Who knows what might happen if someone beats the highest incandescence..</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/cc2e8626229208f9e0d11fd3f8388c87.avif?t=1772203198\" width=1560 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/317549ae8194af3dc0ad33ec58df9f3d.poster.avif?t=1772203198\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/317549ae8194af3dc0ad33ec58df9f3d.webm?t=1772203198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/317549ae8194af3dc0ad33ec58df9f3d.mp4?t=1772203198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add <strong>units </strong>to the shell, which <strong>trigger</strong> their abilities <strong>automatically</strong>. Control the shell to avoid incoming hits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Borrowing from the auto-battler genre, each unit has <strong>abilities</strong>, <strong>classes</strong> and can be <strong>leveled</strong> to gain health and abilities. Unlock <strong>class bonuses</strong> when placing units of the same class. Units are damaged individually. If all units break your <strong>shell shatters</strong> and reveals the <strong>core</strong> – a <strong>second playable character</strong> which without access to unit abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Your shell and units regenerate after a fight, your core does not.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/c9245ac67909bf5bb5526b28a1448ed4.avif?t=1772203198\" width=1560 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/68ed073a080038c64d09755d1f6722fa.poster.avif?t=1772203198\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/68ed073a080038c64d09755d1f6722fa.webm?t=1772203198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/68ed073a080038c64d09755d1f6722fa.mp4?t=1772203198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finishing biomes is no breeze, <strong>60+ enemies, elites and bosses</strong> stand in your way. Defeat bosses and elites for <strong>item crystals</strong> which contain <strong>passive items</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Prepare for heated battles if you want to stand against THE FLAME.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/b7d27a8debce0dda2482781f16793d4f.avif?t=1772203198\" width=1560 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/0599ad457d3fea04cdfa4a84df46fd4b.poster.avif?t=1772203198\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/0599ad457d3fea04cdfa4a84df46fd4b.webm?t=1772203198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/0599ad457d3fea04cdfa4a84df46fd4b.mp4?t=1772203198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>120+ items</strong> can be  found as rewards from elites, bosses and map encounters. Passive items apply <strong>permanent benefits</strong>, consumables trigger <strong>one-time effects</strong>, active items grant <strong>abilities</strong> and <strong>melee weapons</strong> unlock a way of outputting damage actively. Create millions of builds by combining items with your units. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>If you want a shot against THE FLAME, smart choices matter!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/63e1de075a89c25fb306d6bf0bde0a86.avif?t=1772203198\" width=1560 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/afe8d24311e52b9d01d1ea386f4336ee.poster.avif?t=1772203198\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/afe8d24311e52b9d01d1ea386f4336ee.webm?t=1772203198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144460/extras/afe8d24311e52b9d01d1ea386f4336ee.mp4?t=1772203198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Runs and fight are randomly generated</strong>. Select the right path for your build in your pursuit of <strong>THE FLAME</strong>. Choose wisely, as some actions modify the <strong>HEAT LEVEL</strong> - dynamically changing the <strong>difficulty</strong>. Higher heat reaps better rewards, but makes the game harder. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>Will you play it save or risk burning yourself?</i></strong></p>",
